                "invention-title": [
                    "METHOD FOR PRODUCING VANADIUM DIOXIDE THIN FILM AND RAW MATERIAL SOLUTION FOR FORMING VANADIUM DIOXIDE THIN FILM",
                    "二酸化バナジウム薄膜の製造方法及び二酸化バナジウム薄膜形成用原料溶液"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "To provide a method for producing a vanadium dioxide thin film capable of forming a vanadium dioxide thin film having a stoichiometric composition at a calcination temperature of 500°C or less and forming a film on a low melting point material such as general purpose glass.SOLUTION: A method for producing a vanadium dioxide thin film comprises: a step 1 of preparing a raw material solution for forming a vanadium dioxide thin film by adding to a vanadium dioxide precursor at least one stabilizing agent selected from the group consisting of a carboxylic acid having 2 to 10 carbon atoms and a β-diketone having 5 to 11 carbon atoms, and a solvent; a step 2 of forming the film by applying the raw material solution for forming a vanadium dioxide thin film on a base material and performing a preliminary calcination at 250 to 350°C under an inert atmosphere; and after the step 2, a step 3 of performing a main calcination at 450 to 650°C under a gas mixture atmosphere of hydrogen and an inert gas.SELECTED DRAWING: None"
                },
                {
                    "p": "【課題】５００℃以下の焼成温度で化学量論組成を有する二酸化バナジウム薄膜を形成することができ、汎用ガラスなどの低融点材料に成膜可能な二酸化バナジウム薄膜の製造方法を提供する。【解決手段】二酸化バナジウム前駆体に、炭素数２～１０のカルボン酸及び炭素数５～１１のβ－ジケトンからなる群より選択される少なくとも一種の安定化剤、及び、溶剤を添加して二酸化バナジウム薄膜形成用原料溶液を調製する工程１と、前記二酸化バナジウム薄膜形成用原料溶液を基材上に塗布して膜を形成し、不活性雰囲気下に２５０～３５０℃で仮焼成を行う工程２と、前記工程２に続いて、水素と不活性ガスとの混合ガス雰囲気下に、４５０～６５０℃で本焼成を行う工程３とを有する二酸化バナジウム薄膜の製造方法。【選択図】なし"
                }
            ]
